OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1771883656
OL,3,CCumbrian drug dealer jailed for 22
OL,4,Cyears for crystal meth supply plot
OL,6,FA man from Kendal has been jailed for
OL,7,Fplanning a large scale crystal meth
OL,8,Foperation.
OL,10,FDudley Brennan, 31, was sentenced to
OL,11,F22 years and three months in prison at
OL,12,FBolton Crown Court on Monday 23
OL,13,FFebruary.
OL,15,FA search of Brennan's home revealed a
OL,16,Fsmall 'crystal meth' production lab in
OL,17,Fhis kitchen.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/5
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,354,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1771883656
OL,3,CCumbrian drug dealer jailed for 22
OL,4,Cyears for crystal meth supply plot
OL,6,FThe National Crime Agency said that
OL,7,FBrennan believed he could produce as
OL,8,Fmuch as 100 litres of crystal meth in
OL,9,Fa 12-hour period.
OL,11,FHe was also found to have been
OL,12,Fconverting blank firing guns to become
OL,13,Fdeadly weapons.
OL,15,FThe court heard how the 31-year-old
OL,16,Fwas using his motorcycle repairs
OL,17,Fbusiness in the South Cumbrian town to
OL,18,Fmask his criminal activity.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/5
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,354,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1771883656
OL,3,CCumbrian drug dealer jailed for 22
OL,4,Cyears for crystal meth supply plot
OL,6,FBrennan, of Sandes Avenue, Kendal
OL,7,Fconverted at least two submachine guns
OL,8,Fas well as a number of other pistols.
OL,10,FHe was planning to make significant
OL,11,Fprofit by selling these weapons for
OL,12,Fcriminals from Cumbria to Somerset.
OL,14,FOn 7 March 2024, NCA officers raided
OL,15,FBrennan's business after witnessing
OL,16,Fhim taking a delivery.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/5
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,354,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1771883656
OL,3,CCumbrian drug dealer jailed for 22
OL,4,Cyears for crystal meth supply plot
OL,6,FInside the business, NCA officers
OL,7,Fdiscovered a firearms conversion
OL,8,Ffactory and also recovered a Makarov
OL,9,Fstyle semi-automatic pistol which was
OL,10,Fin the process of being converted to
OL,11,Ffire 9mm ammunition, a quantity of
OL,12,Fbullets and a silencer.
OL,14,FNCA branch commander Cat McHugh said:
OL,15,F"I'd like to thank Cheshire Police for
OL,16,Ftheir support, and also Cumbria
OL,17,FPolice, MoD and the other emergency
OL,18,Fservices who helped us that night
OL,19,Fbecause when we went through Brennan's
OL,20,Fdoor we did not know the full extent
OL,21,Fof the threat he posed.
OL,26,@wD@AOU
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/5
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,354,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1771883656
OL,3,CCumbrian drug dealer jailed for 22
OL,4,Cyears for crystal meth supply plot
OL,6,F"Brennan and the group were only
OL,7,Finterested in making money and didn't
OL,8,Fcare at all about the harm these
OL,9,Ffirearms could do in our communities.
OL,10,FThey were a real danger to the public.
OL,12,F"Tackling the criminal use of firearms
OL,13,Fis an NCA priority and we will
OL,14,Fcontinue doing everything in our power
OL,15,Fto achieve that."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUwD@QO]
